<ab facs="#facs_310_r1l30">cʒü <expan>Frankf<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>geſcheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ıſt / . das auch vns <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> wol geviel / . vnd </ab>
